      "body" : "This worked for me, specifically using the &quot;Connection&quot; instance to run:  <code>Statement statement = connection.createStatement();  try {     statement.execute(&quot;set search_path to &#39;&quot; + schema + &quot;&#39;&quot;); } finally {     statement.close(); }</code>"
