    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>If it is possible in your environment, you could also set the user's default schema to your desired schema:</p>\n\n<pre><code>ALTER USER user_name SET search_path to 'schema'\n</code></pre>\n"
