      "comment_id" : 100431946,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "&quot;<i>attempts to connect to a schema</i>&quot; - That&#39;s a bit misleading. The driver does not connect &quot;to a schema&quot;, but to a <i>database</i>. Which schema is used by queries depends on the current setting of the <a href=\"https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/ddl-schemas.html#DDL-SCHEMAS-PATH\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>search_path</code></a>"
    } ],
