    "body" : "<p>In Go with \"sql.DB\" (note the <code>search_path</code> with underscore):</p>\n\n<pre class=\"lang-none prettyprint-override\"><code>postgres://user:password@host/dbname?sslmode=disable&amp;search_path=schema\n</code></pre>\n"
