    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I have tried: currentSchema, searchpath, search_path in the key-value section and nothing works for me.\nI have found work around with the &quot;options&quot; key word:</p>\n<p><code>postgresql://host:port/dbname?options=-c%20search_path%3Dschema_name</code></p>\n"
